											<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
												<p style="text-align: center;">Castle Ladyhawke at Bear Lake Reserve is an 11,000 square foot authentically constructed Scotish border castle offering a destination venue for your dream-come-true wedding…no passport required! Now booking Elopements, Micro-Weddings, Full-Day Weddings and other events of up to 140 guests for 2021, 2022, and 2023; contact our Castle Concierge to book your private tour or request a quote.</p>
