												<p style="text-align: center;">The Bear Lake Reserve mountain lake vacation and real estate community sits nestled in the Blue Ridge Mountains, yet offers all of the comforts of a luxury resort. With stunning mountain views and pristine waters, our secluded community is a hidden gem of western North Carolina. Our numerous amenities allow you the opportunity to do as much or as little as you want to do in a day.</p>
											</div>
